<item>
            <title>[LU-19399] sanity-sec test_12: double free/invalid pointer on lctl nodemap modify</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19399</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Marc Vef &amp;lt;mvef@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7e5d767d-1d9f-4169-a947-c2511da7dd34&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/7e5d767d-1d9f-4169-a947-c2511da7dd34&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_12 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;nodemap squash_uid with 16
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/920&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/920&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-503.40.1.el9_5.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/920&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/920&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-503.40.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;onyx-99vm4: double free or corruption (out)
onyx-99vm4: bash: line 1: 324814 Aborted                 (core dumped) LUSTRE=&quot;/usr/lib64/lustre&quot; bash -c &quot;/usr/sbin/lctl nodemap modify --property squash_uid --name 14853_6 --value 88&quot;
pdsh@onyx-80vm7: onyx-99vm4: ssh exited with exit code 134
CMD: onyx-99vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl nodemap modify --property squash_uid --name 14853_7 --value 88
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-sec test_12 - nodemap squash_uid with 16&lt;/p&gt;</description>
